<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard - LibraTech</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        /* Hide scrollbar for cleaner look */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#FDFBF7] font-sans">
    
    <div class="flex min-h-screen">

        <div class="w-full lg:w-[70%] p-8 lg:p-16 overflow-y-auto">
            
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-12">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1B4D3E] flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-4xl">üèõÔ∏è</span> LibraTech C2
                </h1>
                
                <nav class="flex gap-6 text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    <a href="/" class="text-[#1B4D3E] border-b-2 border-[#1B4D3E] pb-1 transition">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/collection" class="hover:text-[#1B4D3E] transition">Koleksi</a>
                    <a href="/borrowings" class="hover:text-[#1B4D3E] transition">Peminjaman</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition text-orange-500">Tim Kami</a>
                </nav>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[#1B4D3E] text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl mb-12 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">Selamat Datang di<br>Sistem Perpustakaan Digital</h2>
                    <p class="text-green-100 max-w-md mb-8">Kelola koleksi buku, pantau sirkulasi peminjaman, dan administrasi perpustakaan dengan mudah dan efisien.</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <a href="/collection" class="bg-[#D97706] hover:bg-[#b46105] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold shadow-lg transition transform hover:-translate-y-1">Lihat Semua Koleksi</a>
                        <a href="#input-form" class="bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold backdrop-blur-sm transition">Tambah Buku Baru</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-72 h-72 bg-[#D97706]/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] border border-gray-100 text-center">
                    <span class="text-3xl">üìö</span>
                    <h3 class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase mt-2">Total Buku</h3>
                    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1B4D3E] mt-1"><%= books.length %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] border border-gray-100 text-center">
                    <span class="text-3xl">‚è≥</span>
                    <h3 class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase mt-2">Dipinjam</h3>
                    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-600 mt-1">12</p> 
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] border border-gray-100 text-center">
                    <span class="text-3xl">‚úÖ</span>
                    <h3 class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase mt-2">Tersedia</h3>
                     <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mt-1"><%= books.length - 12 %></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="input-form" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-gray-100 mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1B4D3E] mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 border-b pb-4">
                    <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 p-2 rounded-lg">üìñ</span> 
                    Input Buku Terbaru
                </h2>
                
                <form action="/add" method="POST" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="md:col-span-2">
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Judul Buku</label>
                        <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="Masukkan judul lengkap..." required 
                            class="w-full bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-0 ring-1 ring-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706] outline-none transition font-medium">
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Penulis</label>
                        <input type="text" name="author" placeholder="Nama penulis..." required 
                            class="w-full bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-0 ring-1 ring-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706] outline-none transition font-medium">
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Nomor ISBN</label>
                        <input type="text" name="isbn" placeholder="Contoh: 978-..." 
                            class="w-full bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-0 ring-1 ring-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706] outline-none transition font-medium">
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Tahun Terbit</label>
                            <input type="number" name="year_published" placeholder="YYYY" 
                                class="w-full bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-0 ring-1 ring-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706] outline-none transition font-medium">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Stok Awal</label>
                            <input type="number" name="stock" placeholder="Jml" value="1" min="0" 
                                class="w-full bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-0 ring-1 ring-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706] outline-none transition font-medium">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Kategori</label>
                        <select name="category" class="w-full bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-0 ring-1 ring-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706] outline-none transition font-medium appearance-none">
                            <option value="Umum">Umum</option>
                            <option value="Teknologi">Teknologi & Komputer</option>
                            <option value="Sains">Sains & Matematika</option>
                            <option value="Bisnis">Bisnis & Ekonomi</option>
                            <option value="Fiksi">Novel / Fiksi</option>
                            <option value="Sejarah">Sejarah & Budaya</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="md:col-span-2 mt-4">
                        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-[#1B4D3E] hover:bg-[#143d31] text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-green-900/20 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 flex justify-center items-center gap-3">
                            <span>üöÄ</span> Simpan ke Database
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1B4D3E]">Buku Baru Ditambahkan</h2>
                    <a href="/collection" class="text-sm font-bold text-[#D97706] hover:underline">Lihat Semua ‚Üí</a>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
                    <table class="w-full text-left">
                        <thead class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">
                            <tr>
                                <th class="p-5">Judul Buku</th>
                                <th class="p-5 hidden md:table-cell">Kategori</th>
                                <th class="p-5 text-center">Stok</th>
                                <th class="p-5 text-right">Aksi</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
                            <% if(books.length > 0) { %>
                                <% books.forEach(function(book) { %>
                                <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition">
                                    <td class="p-5">
                                        <div class="font-bold text-[#1B4D3E] text-base truncate max-w-xs"><%= book.title %></div>
                                        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1"><%= book.author %></div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="p-5 hidden md:table-cell">
                                        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-600 bg-orange-50 px-2 py-1 rounded-lg">
                                            <%= book.category %>
                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="p-5 text-center font-bold text-gray-700">
                                        <%= book.stock %>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="p-5 text-right">
                                        <a href="/edit/<%= book.id %>" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-[#D97706] font-bold text-sm transition">Edit</a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <% }); %>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <tr><td colspan="4" class="p-8 text-center text-gray-400 italic">Belum ada data buku terbaru.</td></tr>
                            <% } %>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div> <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-[30%] relative bg-cover bg-center sticky top-0 h-screen"
             style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568667256549-094345857637?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop');">
            
             <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1B4D3E] opacity-30 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
            
            <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-10 right-10 text-white p-8 backdrop-blur-md bg-white/10 rounded-3xl border border-white/20">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Explore Knowledge without Limits.</h3>
                <p class="text-green-100 text-sm">LibraTech menyediakan akses mudah ke ribuan sumber daya literasi untuk masa depan yang lebih cerah.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div> </body>
</html>